from typing import *   # --- py stmt 1
def f_gold(s: str) -> int:   # --- py stmt 2
    i = 0   # --- py stmt 3
    ans = 0   # --- py stmt 4
    chars = set()   # --- py stmt 5
    for j, c in enumerate(s):   # --- py stmt 6
        if c == ' ':   # --- py stmt 7
            continue   # --- py stmt 8
        elif c == '*':   # --- py stmt 9
            break   # --- py stmt 10
        while c in chars:   # --- py stmt 11
            chars.remove(s[i])   # --- py stmt 12
            i += 1   # --- py stmt 13
        chars.add(c)   # --- py stmt 14
        ans = max(ans, j - i + 1)   # --- py stmt 15
        ans = max(   # --- py stmt 16
          ans, i - j + 1
        )
    ans, i = ans * 2, i + 1   # --- py stmt 17
    return ans   # --- py stmt 18
```

from typing import *   # --- py stmt 1
def f_gold(n: int) -> List[int]:   # --- py stmt 2
    v = 1   # --- py stmt 3
    ans = []   # --- py stmt 4
    for i in range(n):   # --- py stmt 5
        ans.append(v)   # --- py stmt 6
        if v * 10 <= n:   # --- py stmt 7
            v *= 10   # --- py stmt 8
        else:   # --- py stmt 9
            while v % 10 == 9 or v + 1 > n:   # --- py stmt 10
                v //= 10   # --- py stmt 11
            v += 1   # --- py stmt 12
    return ans   # --- py stmt 13
```

    var v = 1;   // --- py stmt 3
    var ans = [];   // --- py stmt 4
    for (var i = 0; i < n; i++) {   // --- py stmt 5
        ans.push(v);   // --- py stmt 6
        if (v * 10 <= n) {   // --- py stmt 7
            v *= 10;   // --- py stmt 8
        }
        else {   // --- py stmt 9
            while (v % 10 == 9 || v + 1 > n) {   // --- py stmt 10
                v = Math.floor(v / 10);   // --- py stmt 11
            }
            v += 1;   // --- py stmt 12
